{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act18side", "eventName": "塵影餘音", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "LE-4", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "驚愕", "storyInfo": "芙蓉發現感染者病情的變化受到黑鍵與白堊的影響，出言阻止他們上台演出，黑鍵因此前去質問格特魯德。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "28_g6_whitehome", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_knockdoorfast", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（哈欠）", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#6$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來了，來了......", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#6$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......芙蓉？", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "早上好......你起得好早啊，天剛剛亮——", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#6$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 黑鍵呢？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑鍵？黑鍵還在睡啊。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#6$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你眼睛好紅，難道是熬夜了？", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#12$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ——把他也叫起來，趕快。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "28_g2_slumstreets", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "假癒？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我完全聽不懂你想說什麼。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你是真的聽不懂，還是——", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 算了，我再解釋一遍。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我來夕照區，是為了調查這裡感染者異常好轉的現象。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 但根據我們這幾天的走訪，夕照區的感染者並不是好轉，而是“假癒”。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 就是說，病人的狀況看起來好轉了，實際上卻是在惡化。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼明明惡化了，看起來還像是好轉？", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#3$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......我這麼說吧。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 一般來說，身體受到損傷之後，最好的結局是“恢復原狀”。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 如果做不到恢復原狀，身體就會調動沒受損的部分，去補償在損傷中失去的功能，我們一般稱為“代償”。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 現在夕照區的大多數感染者，身體的代償功能都被異常調動起來，導致他們看起來狀態非常好，有的甚至和健康人看不出區別。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 可是，在看不見的地方，在體內，礦石病的感染程度正在快速加深......", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 按照現在的速度，即將有一批人進展到失代償階段了。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "失代償？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 損傷的程度超出了身體最大的代償能力，脆弱的平衡被打破，患者進入礦石病的急性發作期，病情急轉直下，危及生命。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 事實上，已經有人進入急性發作期了。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼會......", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#4$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白你的意思了，但這和我們有什麼關係——", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，難道說白堊也危險了？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 不......", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 問題不在這，根據對調查結果的分析......你和白堊，似乎是引發這一切的主要因素。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和白堊是引發這一切的主要因素？！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在說什麼夢話！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 在分析了你們的行動軌跡之後，我可以確定，你們......或者你們攜帶著的什麼東西，與假癒現象的發生有著極強的相關性。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 比如你們住所隔壁洗衣店的女工，前天還說自己“感覺特別好”，昨天夜裡病情惡化，差點被送進感染者臨終事務處。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我現在懇請你們配合，如果有任何線索，請立刻告訴我！這是為了夕照區所有人的生命安全著想！", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2", "name2": "avg_npc_482_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "黑鍵&白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 完全想不起來嗎？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實想不到。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 以防萬一，你們兩人跟我去一趟辦事處，讓我檢查一下，可以嗎？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "28_g4_embassy", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 從指標上看，一個是再正常不過的健康人，一個是穩定期的礦石病患者......", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 這怎麼可能......", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_501_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_501_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "芙蓉，這次是夕照廳後面樂器店的老闆！", "name": "行板"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_501_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_501_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ——情況如何？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_501_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還好，老闆和高庭區的醫院簽過協議，人已經被接走了。", "name": "行板"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_501_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_501_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 也是假癒？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_501_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，他昨天下午報告的是“沒有任何不適”。", "name": "行板"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_501_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_501_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我去跟進一下，免得醫院方面在協議上耍手段。", "name": "行板"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_501_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_501_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們倆......", "name": "行板"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_501_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_501_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 有我呢。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_501_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我去了！", "name": "行板"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_501_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 300.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我再問一遍，你們有任何能想到的線索嗎？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 現在時間就是生命，拜託了！", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 這樣，黑鍵，你先出來，我們單獨聊聊。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 白堊，你在屋裡等一會兒，好嗎？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "28_g2_slumstreets", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorclosequite"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "單獨把我叫出來是什麼意思？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 如果有誤判的地方我很抱歉，但是......", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我希望你和白堊立刻在空間上分開，越快越好。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼找我，不找他？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你懷疑所謂的“假癒”是我故意所為？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......不。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我確實很希望你就是整件事的罪魁禍首，這樣我就可以直接把你交給維謝海姆的治安官，從根源上解決問題。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 但假癒現象在你到來之前就已經開始，並且被行板注意到了，否則我也不會來維謝海姆，來夕照區。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你憑什麼說——", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等下，在我來之前？那白堊呢？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 假癒現象的出現......就在他來維謝海姆之後。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在他來維謝海姆之後......怎麼會！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 幾乎就是白堊來到夕照區的同時，一部分感染者的指標就開始緩緩變好了。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 但他那時對感染者的影響很微弱，除了細心的行板，沒人發現這一現象。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 等到你們在報名會上相遇之後，白堊的影響陡然增強了。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 按照之前行板發回給羅德島本艦的報告，如果只有白堊，情況惡化到現在這種程度，至少要半年時間。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 你來了之後，短短幾天時間，就......變成了現在這個樣子。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 我需要你向我解釋這到底是怎麼回事。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 如果不能解釋，至少也要在情況變得不可收拾之前踩下刹車。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 所以，我希望你能儘快離開夕照區，離開維謝海姆。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "音樂會呢？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 音樂會——說什麼傻話？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 假如假癒現象是由某種法術引起的，你們的合奏會有很大機率將其增強——", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 難道說......這就是你的......", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#5$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "停。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#5$2"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "實話實說，我非常討厭這種無端受到懷疑的感覺。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 這不是你說討厭就能解決的問題！", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，給我一點時間。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 多長時間？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快的話幾個小時，慢的話......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#9$2"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我不知道，但我保證會來找你的。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 好，我相信你一次。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "28_g4_embassy", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我——我不同意。", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#8$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " ......？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑鍵好不容易才獲得了參加音樂會的資格，好不容易才得到了車爾尼先生的認可......在這種時候半途而廢，實在太可惜了！", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#8$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 這不是認可不認可的問題，是人命關天的大事啊！", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是——", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#7$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 黑鍵？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑鍵，你要去哪？", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#8$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_482_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑鍵！", "name": "白堊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_482_1#8$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您看起來氣喘吁吁，難道是一路跑來的？", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不推薦您用這種方式來找我，暴露的可能性——", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "暴露？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事到如今，您還談什麼暴露？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我問您，您所謂的塵世之音的共振，會不會對其他人造成影響？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "共振？不會。", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要不是刻意驅使，塵世之音的共振不會對人產生任何影響。", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那為什麼芙蓉把我和白堊當成假癒現象的源頭？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "芙蓉？", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#3$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅德島來維謝海姆出差的幹員。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅德島把這種現象稱為“假癒”？不愧是專業人士，精準而簡潔的描述方式。", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#9$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#9$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您......果然知道。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果您說的是最近發生在夕照區的感染者身上的異常現象，我確實知道。", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#2$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到底是怎麼回事？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一言以蔽之，白堊體內的塵世之音是損壞的。", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "損壞的？？？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在您施展法術時，體內的塵世之音會被啟動，為您提供幫助，沒錯吧？", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，我確實會在施術時隱約聽見一段刺耳的旋律，但這種東西怎麼可能損壞？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白堊的塵世之音一直處在異常啟動的狀態，不存在如您現在一般“關閉”的狀況。", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "換句話說，他一直在不自覺地向周圍施術，而他自己無法控制這件事。", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你去問他，他很可能會說，他一直都能隱約聽見某種旋律。", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您可以將這種現象理解為“洩漏”。", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#2$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#12$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所謂“假癒”，就是他的塵世之音洩漏的後果——無差別地提高周圍的源石活性，利用源石的能量“治癒”周圍的感染者......", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#12$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#12$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只不過，用以治癒感染者的能量之源，是感染者自己體內的源石。", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#12$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#12$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以感染者自己為法術裝置，以他們體內的源石為能源，增進他們的代償功能......這就是白堊的塵世之音引發的“假癒”。", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#12$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大概從很久以前，白堊就一直保持著這樣的狀態，一直在影響著周圍的感染者了。", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果一直都是這樣，他的異常早就應該被人發現了！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是您的功勞了，黑鍵先生。", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#7$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我？！", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "共振。", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#10$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......共振增強了白堊塵世之音的洩漏，所以假癒現象才會在這幾天集中爆發？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "完全正確。", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#10$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#2$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我完全明白了。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#2$2"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#10$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我退出您的這場計畫。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您就這麼放棄了唾手可得的自由？", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還沒瘋到用一整個地塊的感染者換自由的地步。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您被羅德島的人嚇住了。", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#2$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "假癒確實談不上是好事，但您和白堊的音樂會幾天後就要舉行了。", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等到這幾天過去，您的塵世之音被除掉，然後再離開維謝海姆，也不會多死幾個感染者的。", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣的機會千載難逢，您現在走了，烏提卡伯爵這個身份就將跟您一輩子。", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#8$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您真的想這樣嗎？", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#5$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不想，但我不能那麼做。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#5$2"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再見，格特魯德女士。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您要去哪裡？", "name": "格特魯德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_484_1#6$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_484_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跟您無關。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}